{"tid":1191504,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"聽日有咩理由唔出嚟遊行？","createTime":"2019-06-08T03:25:36.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-08T03:53:50.000Z","uid":9888,"like":18,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"231b29b57df89e6fa9d7a05713eeff371832bdbd","tid":1191504,"uid":9888,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-08T03:25:36.000Z","msg":"香港人 如果俾人逼到咁樣 你都唔上街 真係自己攞嚟<br />\n聽日上街係責任嚟 <br />\n<br />\n問好多朋友去唔去 有啲話實去 有啲話唔去 之後話2014年佔領完 最後都係一堆人坐監 <br />\n<br />\n咁又點？坐監代表佢地做錯？ 根本就係政治打壓<br />\n政府就係想你驚 <br />\n<br />\n從來大部分政治上嘅抗爭都係好長時間 <br />\n香港人就係衰在懶 心急 無耐性 又唔想付出 成日想坐享其成 <br />\n覺得當刻失敗咗 就會放棄<br />\n見到人坐監 又會淆底 <br />\n但我相信公道自在人心 而曾經為過香港付出嘅人都會得到回報 <br />\n<br />\n只要香港人肯爭氣 肯聯成一線 就會有希望<br />\n<br />\n我想講 依然好多香港人熱愛自己嘅城市 會守護我城<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ECR60KH.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FECR60KH.gif&h=27e2d21f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n聽日見！<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/5GyryRRL-NY\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F5GyryRRL-NY&d=Bm7f%2FS52JQW29R4IancW89%2BR0LtvndqJ8lr%2BzYsHiyM%3D&h=6fa64038\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/5GyryRRL-NY</a>"},{"pid":"7d14c9e3ccc6664ad40f3a0dd256c1e328dba082","tid":1191504,"uid":19454,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-08T03:27:16.000Z","msg":"住緊公屋、拎綜援果班<br />\n<br />\n（佔大部份人口）"},{"pid":"6c40df411d55e922de4483ba327bfad03e9b215a","tid":1191504,"uid":191815,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-08T03:27:21.000Z","msg":"冇達哥睇咪唔撚去囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e6295615b313d63c902e765eab876269d05a54f9","tid":1191504,"uid":249885,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-08T03:28:49.000Z","msg":"坐監我屋企人點算"},{"pid":"90845031a8d49273ca8accdf22d959fa3e1c6a5c","tid":1191504,"uid":51701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7d14c9e3ccc6664ad40f3a0dd256c1e328dba082","tid":1191504,"uid":19454,"like":1,"dislike"